Package net.etfbl.pj2.model

Class Rental

java.lang.Object
net.etfbl.pj2.model.Rental
public class Rental extends Object
Represents a rental transaction. Each rental has a user, vehicle ID, start and end location, start and end time, duration in seconds, promotion status, discount status, and breakdown status.
Since:
2.6.2024.

  • Constructor Details

    • Rental

      public Rental(String username, String vehicleId, Field startLocation, Field endLocation, LocalDateTime startTime, Long durationInSeconds, Boolean isPromotion, Boolean isBreakdown)
      Constructs a new Rental object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      username - The username of the user renting the vehicle.
      vehicleId - The ID of the rented vehicle.
      startLocation - The start location of the rental.
      endLocation - The end location of the rental.
      startTime - The start time of the rental.
      durationInSeconds - The duration of the rental in seconds.
      isPromotion - The promotion status of the rental.
      isBreakdown - The breakdown status of the rental.
